WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:36.230 --> 00:00:40.650
<i>Many moons have passed since the Imperial 
Army went to war with the Hellhorde.</i>

3
00:00:41.470 --> 00:00:46.410
<i>I am Ex, a sentient sacred blade 
passed down in the Royal Empire.</i>

4
00:00:47.130 --> 00:00:49.490
<i>Having fallen into the 
hands of the Hellhorde,</i>

5
00:00:49.490 --> 00:00:53.770
<i>I find myself imprisoned with 
my master, Her Highness.</i>

6
00:01:00.110 --> 00:01:01.490
Is that so?

7
00:01:02.510 --> 00:01:06.110
If you refuse to reveal the 
Royal Empire's secrets...

8
00:01:06.790 --> 00:01:10.090
We will have to subject you 
to full-blown torture.

9
00:01:11.550 --> 00:01:12.600
Wait!

10
00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.130
Laws regarding prisoners of war
 prohibit the use of torture!

11
00:01:15.130 --> 00:01:17.180
Those are human laws, are they not?

12
00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:19.080
Damn you...

13
00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:20.880
Rest assured, Ex.

14
00:01:21.430 --> 00:01:25.120
I would never give in to their torture!

15
00:01:26.770 --> 00:01:28.260
Your Highness!

16
00:01:31.410 --> 00:01:32.910
In that case...

17
00:01:33.290 --> 00:01:36.550
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

18
00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:07.950
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

19
00:03:08.540 --> 00:03:10.410
10 Minutes Ago

20
00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:15.420
An experimental spell went haywire, 
and Her Highness lost her memories.

21
00:03:15.750 --> 00:03:19.430
It seems she doesn't remember anything 
since she was taken prisoner.

22
00:03:19.860 --> 00:03:23.770
Since it was caused by a rogue spell, 
we don't know how to treat it.

23
00:03:23.770 --> 00:03:24.880
Oh, no...

24
00:03:26.180 --> 00:03:30.250
I have no memories, but it seems 
that several months have passed,

25
00:03:30.250 --> 00:03:33.400
and I have been subjected to 
torture on a daily basis.

26
00:03:33.720 --> 00:03:37.180
But thus far, the Hellhorde have 
yet to launch their attack.

27
00:03:38.130 --> 00:03:42.260
It seems that I haven't succumbed 
to your torture a single time!

28
00:03:42.820 --> 00:03:45.660
Um, well, about that...

29
00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:50.080
It's uncertain what may trigger 
her memories coming back,

30
00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:54.030
so the doctor said it'd be best 
to return to her daily routine.

31
00:03:54.300 --> 00:03:58.040
And thus, going back to the very beginning...

32
00:04:00.890 --> 00:04:04.100
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

33
00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:07.590
That's right.

34
00:04:07.590 --> 00:04:10.210
Her memory loss may have come as a shock,

35
00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:10.770
Dumb Face-o-Meter

36
00:04:10.210 --> 00:04:13.630
but this isn't Her Highness who's 
used to giving in every single time.

37
00:04:14.230 --> 00:04:16.540
She's back to being the old Princess!

38
00:04:16.540 --> 00:04:21.020
The one who's survived countless battles 
and achieved many a great feat!

39
00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:26.350
She very well might be able 
to resist this torture!

40
00:04:27.530 --> 00:04:29.280
Looks yummy...

41
00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:30.570
Nope, she's gonna cave!

42
00:04:31.370 --> 00:04:33.000
D-Don't get me wrong, Ex!

43
00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:35.020
I'm not feeling tempted at all!

44
00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:37.000
I simply gave my honest impression 
of how good it looks!

45
00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:39.200
All human beings would feel the same way!

46
00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:38.810
I've heard this before.

47
00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:45.000
I would never give in to 
the likes of mere toast!

48
00:04:55.080 --> 00:04:56.360
I've seen this before.

49
00:04:56.750 --> 00:04:58.930
<i>I-I can hear it!</i>

50
00:04:58.930 --> 00:05:00.170
<i>It sounds...</i>

51
00:05:00.170 --> 00:05:01.820
<i>It sounds so tasty!</i>

52
00:05:03.730 --> 00:05:06.060
Hang in there, Your Highness!

53
00:05:07.550 --> 00:05:09.310
Don't worry, Ex.

54
00:05:10.180 --> 00:05:15.960
I am Commander of the Imperial Third Legion.

55
00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:19.500
I-I will never give in...

56
00:05:19.800 --> 00:05:21.680
to your pathetic torture!

57
00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:23.580
The same reaction as 
season one, episode one!

58
00:05:23.950 --> 00:05:26.510
The torture isn't over yet.

59
00:05:26.510 --> 00:05:27.710
Is that...

60
00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.550
Very              Yummy

61
00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.550
Honey

62
00:05:28.170 --> 00:05:29.550
'Tis honey.

63
00:05:29.550 --> 00:05:30.470
You wouldn't dare!

64
00:05:30.860 --> 00:05:32.090
You fiend!

65
00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:48.200
That <i>has</i> to taste amazing!

66
00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:50.630
<i>I will reveal my secret!</i>

67
00:05:50.630 --> 00:05:53.140
<i>I caved. All that's left is to go to sleep.</i>

68
00:05:50.830 --> 00:05:52.660
<i>So yummy!</i>

69
00:05:52.660 --> 00:05:57.450
<i>I'll talk!</i>

70
00:06:00.540 --> 00:06:04.250
M-My head!

71
00:06:02.590 --> 00:06:03.550
Your Highness?!

72
00:06:03.550 --> 00:06:04.690
Your Highness!

73
00:06:04.690 --> 00:06:05.760
Y-Your High...

74
00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:08.450
I-Is something wrong?

75
00:06:11.520 --> 00:06:16.850
The moment I was about to give in, 
the memories all came flooding back.

76
00:06:16.850 --> 00:06:17.760
What?

77
00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:19.580
Your Highness, does that mean...

78
00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:21.090
Yes!

79
00:06:21.570 --> 00:06:23.450
My memories have returned!

80
00:06:24.600 --> 00:06:25.940
Your Highness!

81
00:06:29.010 --> 00:06:30.840
You've regained your memories.

82
00:06:30.840 --> 00:06:34.190
There's no information that 
could be more valuable.

83
00:06:34.190 --> 00:06:38.030
In other words, you've told us your 
secret, and we're done with you!

84
00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:41.040
'Tis time for a toast party!

85
00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:42.700
Yay!

86
00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:47.970
It's as yummy as ever!

87
00:06:47.970 --> 00:06:50.980
Untz, untz, untz!

88
00:06:50.050 --> 00:06:52.460
I've seen this before as well.

89
00:06:50.980 --> 00:06:55.210
Untz, untz, untz, untz!

90
00:06:55.210 --> 00:07:01.050
Untz, untz, untz, untz, untz, untz!

91
00:06:58.600 --> 00:07:01.060
The princess went 
back to normal

92
00:07:28.310 --> 00:07:29.630
Your Majesty.

93
00:07:36.460 --> 00:07:40.940
I'm glad to hear her memories returned.

94
00:07:44.790 --> 00:07:48.610
I have one additional matter to report on.

95
00:07:49.260 --> 00:07:50.510
Go on.

96
00:07:51.060 --> 00:07:55.490
We've noticed changes to the official 
website for the anime Your Majesty is fond of.

97
00:07:55.490 --> 00:07:56.680
Oh?

98
00:07:59.260 --> 00:08:03.950
I appreciate the periodic updates 
even after it's gone off the air.

99
00:08:03.950 --> 00:08:05.210
What?!

100
00:08:05.210 --> 00:08:08.210
Season 2 Confirmed!!

101
00:08:05.530 --> 00:08:07.930
They're making a season two of the anime?!

102
00:08:08.210 --> 00:08:14.770
Hell yes!

103
00:08:17.850 --> 00:08:20.350
Congrats on Season 2

104
00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:20.350
A cake!

105
00:08:20.350 --> 00:08:22.130
Looks tasty!

106
00:08:22.520 --> 00:08:26.090
An anime His Majesty likes will 
be getting a second season.

107
00:08:26.090 --> 00:08:30.290
To celebrate, we're distributing 
cakes all across Hellholm.

108
00:08:30.290 --> 00:08:32.390
Oh, good for him.

109
00:08:32.390 --> 00:08:34.140
An anime that the Hell-Lord likes?

110
00:08:35.160 --> 00:08:36.440
I see!

111
00:08:36.440 --> 00:08:40.490
This is a torture where I must reveal 
the empire's secret if I want cake!

112
00:08:40.490 --> 00:08:43.540
No, the cake is from His Majesty.

113
00:08:43.540 --> 00:08:45.180
'Tisn't torture.

114
00:08:45.180 --> 00:08:46.250
Really?

115
00:08:47.740 --> 00:08:49.290
Let's enjoy it together.

116
00:08:49.290 --> 00:08:50.650
Yay!

117
00:08:53.530 --> 00:08:55.300
You're putting candles on it?

118
00:08:55.300 --> 00:08:56.180
Indeed.

119
00:08:56.180 --> 00:09:00.250
Can I be the one to blow out the candles?

120
00:09:01.510 --> 00:09:06.260
There's no greater moment of joy than 
blowing out the flame on a candle.

121
00:09:06.260 --> 00:09:08.220
Yeah! I love it!

122
00:09:08.520 --> 00:09:09.850
Which is why you mustn't.

123
00:09:14.470 --> 00:09:15.580
What?

124
00:09:15.580 --> 00:09:21.350
If you wish to blow out the candles, 
you'll have to tell us an imperial secret.

125
00:09:21.350 --> 00:09:25.410
Y-You said the cake wasn't torture...

126
00:09:25.410 --> 00:09:26.770
That's true.

127
00:09:26.770 --> 00:09:28.970
The cake isn't torture.

128
00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:31.820
The cake itself, that is.

129
00:09:32.110 --> 00:09:36.250
You monster!

130
00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:36.250
It's like being back home!

131
00:09:36.260 --> 00:09:39.050
Congrats on Season 2

132
00:09:40.350 --> 00:09:43.560
Congratulations on season two!

133
00:09:43.020 --> 00:09:44.520
She started singing?!

134
00:09:43.910 --> 00:09:47.280
Congratulations on season two!

135
00:09:44.510 --> 00:09:47.760
<i>If I don't yield to the torture 
before Torture stops singing,</i>

136
00:09:47.510 --> 00:09:51.680
Congratulations on season two!

137
00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:50.270
<i>I'll lose the right to blow out the candles?</i>

138
00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:52.770
<i>Damn it all!</i>

139
00:09:52.180 --> 00:09:56.060
Congratulations on season two!

140
00:09:52.770 --> 00:09:55.770
<i>I get so excited hearing this melody!</i>

141
00:09:55.770 --> 00:09:58.310
<i>It makes me want to blow out those candles!</i>

142
00:09:57.030 --> 00:10:00.540
Congratulations on season two!

143
00:09:58.320 --> 00:10:00.690
Your Highness! Stay strong!

144
00:10:00.690 --> 00:10:02.580
You only need to bear 
it until the song ends!

145
00:10:00.850 --> 00:10:04.210
Congratulations on season two!

146
00:10:02.970 --> 00:10:05.620
I know it must pain you, but 
all things come to an end!

147
00:10:04.490 --> 00:10:05.630
Congratulations...

148
00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:07.410
Every storm runs out of rain!

149
00:10:07.410 --> 00:10:10.250
Well, it sucks now standing in the rain!

150
00:10:10.250 --> 00:10:13.750
Congratulations on season two!

151
00:10:13.940 --> 00:10:16.210
<i>This is the final refrain.</i>

152
00:10:14.060 --> 00:10:17.460
Congratulations on season two!

153
00:10:16.210 --> 00:10:17.460
<i>The song's about to end!</i>

154
00:10:17.780 --> 00:10:21.100
Congratulations on season two!

155
00:10:17.990 --> 00:10:20.860
<i>Just a little longer, and 
I'll reign victorious!</i>

156
00:10:21.310 --> 00:10:25.520
Congratulations on season two!

157
00:10:21.750 --> 00:10:22.560
<i>Endure!</i>

158
00:10:22.970 --> 00:10:24.010
<i>Endure!</i>

159
00:10:24.300 --> 00:10:26.300
<i>You can endure it!</i>

160
00:10:26.300 --> 00:10:30.900
Congratulations on season two!

161
00:10:36.700 --> 00:10:38.770
<i>It's over!</i>

162
00:10:39.210 --> 00:10:41.860
<i>Yay! I endured it!</i>

163
00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:43.760
<i>I endured it until the end!</i>

164
00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:44.680
<i>Take that!</i>

165
00:10:44.680 --> 00:10:47.560
<i>I'm Commander of the Imperial Third Legion!</i>

166
00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:50.480
<i>Your lousy torture was no match for...</i>

167
00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:53.600
<i>Oh, no!</i>

168
00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:56.430
<i>Yes, I'd forgotten!</i>

169
00:10:56.430 --> 00:10:59.840
<i>You don't actually blow out the 
candles until the song's over!</i>

170
00:10:59.840 --> 00:11:03.030
<i>There was no point in enduring 
it while she was singing!</i>

171
00:11:03.330 --> 00:11:05.820
<i>The real battle starts here and now!</i>

172
00:11:03.340 --> 00:11:07.640
Congrats on Season 2

173
00:11:05.820 --> 00:11:07.770
<i>The moment after the song has just ended!</i>

174
00:11:07.640 --> 00:11:11.020
Congrats on Season 2

175
00:11:07.770 --> 00:11:10.440
<i>The moment they're just 
begging to be blown out!</i>

176
00:11:12.050 --> 00:11:13.880
<i>Oh, it's no use...</i>

177
00:11:14.280 --> 00:11:17.710
<i>Because I wrongly believed I was done 
enduring it when the song ended...</i>

178
00:11:19.460 --> 00:11:23.320
<i>My mind's gone completely loosey-goosey...</i>

179
00:11:21.570 --> 00:11:24.120
Loosey-Goosey Mind

180
00:11:24.530 --> 00:11:26.350
<i>With my mind like this...</i>

181
00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:31.510
Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!

182
00:11:26.860 --> 00:11:30.210
<i>I can't resist the urge 
to blow out the candles!</i>

183
00:11:26.870 --> 00:11:30.200
Urge to Blow Out Candles

184
00:11:31.510 --> 00:11:32.620
Ready...

185
00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:35.690
Heave-ho! Heave-ho!

186
00:11:35.690 --> 00:11:37.760
Heave-ho!

187
00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:40.560
<i>There's no way I could win!</i>

188
00:11:41.130 --> 00:11:43.130
Congrats on Season 2

189
00:11:48.680 --> 00:11:50.800
I'm happy for you, Your Highness!

190
00:11:51.670 --> 00:11:54.130
Come, let us all have a slice.

191
00:11:54.130 --> 00:11:55.530
Yay!

192
00:11:55.940 --> 00:11:59.230
The princess 
confessed

193
00:12:00.420 --> 00:12:01.740
Your Majesty.

194
00:12:02.570 --> 00:12:05.490
The secret we obtained from the princess...

195
00:12:05.910 --> 00:12:09.070
It seems that their king 
will turn fifty this year.

196
00:12:09.470 --> 00:12:11.120
Oh?

197
00:12:13.650 --> 00:12:17.210
He's a great deal older than I am.

198
00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:23.970
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

199
00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:29.930
<i>The princess and Hell-Lord unexpectedly 
found themselves in another world.</i>

200
00:12:30.310 --> 00:12:35.730
<i>However, one thing led to another, and they 
managed to return to their original world.</i>

201
00:12:37.150 --> 00:12:39.930
Let's take it from the top...

202
00:12:42.320 --> 00:12:45.310
And play some basketball!

203
00:12:47.820 --> 00:12:52.240
The Hellholm basketball matchup 
is about to get underway!

204
00:12:52.540 --> 00:12:54.050
This is Gilga with the play-by-play,

205
00:12:54.050 --> 00:12:56.490
and Ex as our color analyst!

206
00:12:56.800 --> 00:12:58.920
First, we have Team Princess.

207
00:12:59.350 --> 00:13:03.090
With their captain, Princess, at the core, 
this is a team with plenty of agility.

208
00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:05.590
Power Forward: Princess

209
00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:05.590
Point Guard: Torture

210
00:13:01.340 --> 00:13:05.590
Center: Krall

211
00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:05.590
Shooting Guard: Inki

212
00:13:03.090 --> 00:13:05.180
Will we see them put up big points?

213
00:13:04.340 --> 00:13:05.590
Small Forward: Vanilla

214
00:13:05.780 --> 00:13:07.790
Now for Team Hell-Lord.

215
00:13:08.090 --> 00:13:11.580
Their powerful defense are 
sure to keep scores low!

216
00:13:08.930 --> 00:13:13.770
Center: Hell-Lord

217
00:13:08.930 --> 00:13:13.770
Point Guard: Giant

218
00:13:10.930 --> 00:13:13.770
Power Forward: Datarma

219
00:13:11.580 --> 00:13:14.880
Can we expect Princess Maomao-chan 
as their leading scorer?

220
00:13:13.140 --> 00:13:13.770
Shooting Guard: Kanadge

221
00:13:13.850 --> 00:13:15.730
Small Forward:
 Maomao-chan

222
00:13:15.710 --> 00:13:18.980
Maomao-chan! Good luck!

223
00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:18.980
Queen 
Lulune

224
00:13:18.980 --> 00:13:21.310
But why basketball, of all things?

225
00:13:21.310 --> 00:13:24.350
Basketball's big right now in Hellholm.

226
00:13:24.350 --> 00:13:25.990
Oh, is that right?

227
00:13:26.300 --> 00:13:30.130
No one really knows the rules, 
so they just go by vibes.

228
00:13:30.130 --> 00:13:31.520
Wait, will this be okay?

229
00:13:32.760 --> 00:13:35.280
The game's about to start!

230
00:13:35.910 --> 00:13:38.500
The referee, Youki, was on 
her school basketball team,

231
00:13:38.500 --> 00:13:40.630
making her the only one who 
vaguely knows the rules!

232
00:13:40.630 --> 00:13:42.640
Know all the rules if you were on the team!

233
00:13:42.640 --> 00:13:44.870
I may have been on the basketball team,

234
00:13:45.150 --> 00:13:50.050
but I was mostly busy playing in the gym 
and chatting at family restaurants!

235
00:13:50.280 --> 00:13:53.880
Don't assume all basketball team 
members know how to play basketball!

236
00:13:53.880 --> 00:13:55.440
Why the high-and-mighty act?

237
00:13:55.810 --> 00:13:57.800
We're finally starting the game!

238
00:13:57.800 --> 00:13:59.880
Both teams have their players in position.

239
00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:01.660
And now...

240
00:14:01.930 --> 00:14:03.240
The kickoff!

241
00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:04.780
It's called a tip-off in basketball.

242
00:14:07.530 --> 00:14:08.800
Hngy-Baby!

243
00:14:10.990 --> 00:14:12.660
Super Sixth Man: Hngy

244
00:14:13.470 --> 00:14:14.650
What?!

245
00:14:15.380 --> 00:14:16.820
Whoa!

246
00:14:16.820 --> 00:14:19.320
Some stunning teamwork to 
make up for their height!

247
00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:20.940
Ref, that's clearly against the rules!

248
00:14:20.940 --> 00:14:21.460
Eh?

249
00:14:21.460 --> 00:14:23.230
Nice one, Hngy-Baby!

250
00:14:22.330 --> 00:14:24.960
Krall showing Hngy some love!

251
00:14:25.430 --> 00:14:27.540
Princess not missing the catch.

252
00:14:28.190 --> 00:14:30.350
Team Princess has first possession!

253
00:14:30.930 --> 00:14:33.730
Now, first we see them go by the playbook...

254
00:14:33.730 --> 00:14:36.050
with everyone surrounding the ball!

255
00:14:36.050 --> 00:14:37.300
Is this gym class basketball?

256
00:14:37.300 --> 00:14:41.100
Princess stuck in the crowd, 
unable to move the ball!

257
00:14:41.100 --> 00:14:43.310
They're just asking for a foul to happen!

258
00:14:43.490 --> 00:14:45.600
Princess, pass the ball to me!

259
00:14:45.600 --> 00:14:47.820
I wanna dribble the ball, too!

260
00:14:47.820 --> 00:14:50.780
Hey, you're all putting 
pressure on Princess-chan!

261
00:14:50.780 --> 00:14:54.150
Princess-chan, take a load 
off and let go of the ball!

262
00:14:54.920 --> 00:14:56.940
I've got you, Princess!

263
00:14:56.940 --> 00:14:59.690
Go for it, Maomao-chan!

264
00:15:00.690 --> 00:15:02.580
<i>Since it's come down to this...</i>

265
00:15:05.290 --> 00:15:07.340
Princess with the bold attempt!

266
00:15:07.340 --> 00:15:08.670
I admire the spirit!

267
00:15:09.890 --> 00:15:11.420
Sadly, it ends in a steal!

268
00:15:14.050 --> 00:15:16.760
His Majesty goes straight for the long pass!

269
00:15:16.760 --> 00:15:17.560
Oh, no, you don't!

270
00:15:22.980 --> 00:15:25.180
Are you hurt, Vanilla-chan?

271
00:15:25.690 --> 00:15:27.570
Princess!

272
00:15:29.270 --> 00:15:33.030
Wow! Kanadge drives to 
the basket by himself!

273
00:15:33.030 --> 00:15:34.920
He's completely open!

274
00:15:34.920 --> 00:15:35.840
See!

275
00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:37.790
This is what happens when you 
all swarm the ball!

276
00:15:39.320 --> 00:15:41.430
The left hand is just 
for holding the ball...

277
00:15:43.650 --> 00:15:46.470
Oh, but he's denied by the goal post!

278
00:15:46.470 --> 00:15:47.980
He just totally sucks at basketball!

279
00:15:47.980 --> 00:15:49.470
Princess with the hard defense!

280
00:15:49.850 --> 00:15:50.880
Everyone!

281
00:15:51.180 --> 00:15:52.640
Get into square formation!

282
00:15:52.640 --> 00:15:54.140
Yeah!

283
00:15:56.150 --> 00:15:57.650
Whoa!

284
00:15:57.650 --> 00:16:00.080
They're holding hands and 
surrounding Princess!

285
00:16:00.080 --> 00:16:02.200
Slowly making their way to the basket!

286
00:16:02.200 --> 00:16:04.250
Team Hell-Lord can't touch them!

287
00:16:04.250 --> 00:16:06.020
Is this allowed in the rules?!

288
00:16:06.940 --> 00:16:08.890
Oh! A dribbling mistake!

289
00:16:08.890 --> 00:16:09.450
Oh, no!

290
00:16:09.450 --> 00:16:12.310
Torture kicks the ball away!

291
00:16:12.310 --> 00:16:16.280
Kanadge grabs the loose ball, and 
quickly gets ready to shoot!

292
00:16:16.740 --> 00:16:18.990
Yeah, I'm Kanadge.

293
00:16:18.990 --> 00:16:21.040
The guy who never gives up till the end.

294
00:16:22.190 --> 00:16:24.580
Check out that fadeaway!

295
00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:26.250
A staple of basketball manga,

296
00:16:26.250 --> 00:16:28.570
where you take a shot jumping 
backward to evade defenders!

297
00:16:28.570 --> 00:16:30.170
Why now, when you're wide open?

298
00:16:30.790 --> 00:16:33.070
Denied yet again by the goal post!

299
00:16:33.070 --> 00:16:35.890
Also, a basketball hoop 
isn't a goal post!

300
00:16:37.050 --> 00:16:43.880
<i>The fierce battle between Team Hell-Lord 
and Team Princess continued...</i>

301
00:16:46.900 --> 00:16:49.120
That's the end of the game!

302
00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:52.590
Team Hell-Lord takes it 
with a score of 6 to 4!

303
00:16:52.590 --> 00:16:53.900
A score you'd see in baseball.

304
00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:55.860
Did you have fun playing basketball?

305
00:16:55.860 --> 00:16:56.730
Yeah!

306
00:16:56.730 --> 00:16:58.400
I want to play again with everyone!

307
00:16:58.400 --> 00:17:00.660
Who's up for the family 
restaurant after this?

308
00:17:00.660 --> 00:17:01.690
Me.

309
00:17:01.690 --> 00:17:03.150
I'm in!

310
00:17:04.260 --> 00:17:06.730
<i>Everyone's going to a family restaurant?</i>

311
00:17:06.730 --> 00:17:07.830
Here!

312
00:17:08.260 --> 00:17:10.600
Vanilla-chan and I are coming, too.

313
00:17:10.600 --> 00:17:11.330
What?

314
00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:12.780
Right?

315
00:17:14.670 --> 00:17:15.670
Yeah!

316
00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:17.940
Princess-chan, we're leaving now.

317
00:17:17.940 --> 00:17:19.860
Good work out there, Your Highness.

318
00:17:21.570 --> 00:17:23.000
We lost, huh?

319
00:17:23.910 --> 00:17:29.810
Still, playing basketball today made 
me remember the most important thing.

320
00:17:30.070 --> 00:17:31.150
What?

321
00:17:31.650 --> 00:17:34.130
My love for the game of basketball!

322
00:17:34.130 --> 00:17:36.570
You never had any love
 for it in the first place!

323
00:17:36.570 --> 00:17:37.610
Nope!

324
00:17:39.860 --> 00:17:41.860
Are you all right, Torture?

325
00:17:43.540 --> 00:17:44.850
Don't mind me.

326
00:17:44.850 --> 00:17:48.220
It seems I got a bit carried 
away in all the fun.

327
00:17:49.330 --> 00:17:50.930
I've never been very athletic.

328
00:17:50.930 --> 00:17:55.260
Hey, are you going to be good for 
today's torture in that sorry state?

329
00:17:55.260 --> 00:17:58.230
Perhaps not.

330
00:17:59.670 --> 00:18:03.680
Looks like today will be 
a surefire win for me!

331
00:18:04.350 --> 00:18:08.900
<i>The torture went as planned, 
and the princess confessed.</i>

332
00:18:09.240 --> 00:18:12.170
<i>And they all went to a family restaurant.</i>

333
00:18:12.900 --> 00:18:16.900
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

334
00:18:19.280 --> 00:18:22.780
I'm confident that I won't 
yield to today's torture!

335
00:18:25.050 --> 00:18:26.770
Aren't you dying to know why?

336
00:18:26.770 --> 00:18:27.490
No...

337
00:18:27.710 --> 00:18:31.280
Because I spent the whole day taking 
action to prepare for the torture!

338
00:18:31.280 --> 00:18:33.250
Not even letting me answer, huh?!

339
00:18:33.480 --> 00:18:35.210
And what action do I mean?

340
00:18:35.210 --> 00:18:37.610
Visualizing it in my head!

341
00:18:37.610 --> 00:18:42.680
You know, when you run mental simulations 
to hone your techniques and tactics.

342
00:18:42.680 --> 00:18:48.220
At my advanced skill level, it provides 
almost as much experience as the real thing.

343
00:18:48.580 --> 00:18:52.510
I employed this method to 
visualize our torture sessions.

344
00:18:52.510 --> 00:18:53.590
I see.

345
00:18:53.590 --> 00:18:55.990
You <i>did</i> seem awfully quiet today.

346
00:18:55.990 --> 00:18:57.330
Yep.

347
00:18:57.330 --> 00:19:00.980
I was subjected to torture 
over and over in my mind.

348
00:19:01.070 --> 00:19:03.700
Lunchtime

349
00:19:07.030 --> 00:19:09.960
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

350
00:19:10.290 --> 00:19:12.380
Today's torture is...

351
00:19:12.380 --> 00:19:13.670
Macaroni gratin!

352
00:19:13.670 --> 00:19:15.080
The queen is fond of fruits!

353
00:19:15.080 --> 00:19:16.790
Butter soy sauce pasta with scallops!

354
00:19:16.790 --> 00:19:18.410
My little sister loves skiing!

355
00:19:18.410 --> 00:19:20.130
Fluffy ricotta pancakes!

356
00:19:20.130 --> 00:19:22.130
Jimochi collects miniature cars!

357
00:19:22.130 --> 00:19:22.970
Plum

358
00:19:22.130 --> 00:19:22.970
Gum!

359
00:19:22.970 --> 00:19:26.210
The sacred blade Machina is hidden 
in the Fountain of Dharma!

360
00:19:28.470 --> 00:19:33.930
Doing this gave me plenty of combat 
experience to come up with countermeasures.

361
00:19:33.930 --> 00:19:37.140
Did I imagine those flashbacks of you 
vigorously giving up in seconds flat?!

362
00:19:38.030 --> 00:19:42.060
Also, this is the first I've heard of 
Sir Jimochi collecting car miniatures.

363
00:19:42.060 --> 00:19:42.870
Oh.

364
00:19:42.870 --> 00:19:46.520
He used to always stop by the toy 
store on our way home from training.

365
00:19:46.530 --> 00:19:54.540
Line Ends Here

366
00:19:46.830 --> 00:19:52.050
End of the line for the special limited 
edition car miniature releasing today!

367
00:19:50.210 --> 00:19:52.040
Oh, fidget, fidget.

368
00:19:52.050 --> 00:19:54.550
Hey, are we done yet?

369
00:19:52.210 --> 00:19:54.040
Oh, fidget, fidget.

370
00:19:54.900 --> 00:19:57.370
Are you here to buy one 
for your granddaughter?

371
00:19:57.370 --> 00:19:58.420
No.

372
00:19:58.810 --> 00:20:00.810
This is my hobby!

373
00:20:00.710 --> 00:20:04.720
Honored Knight
Jimochi

374
00:20:00.810 --> 00:20:04.390
I was so excited, I didn't 
sleep a wink last night.

375
00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:05.880
I see...

376
00:20:05.880 --> 00:20:08.600
Fidget, fidget.

377
00:20:06.730 --> 00:20:08.600
That old fart again!

378
00:20:08.860 --> 00:20:10.480
Fear not, Ex.

379
00:20:10.480 --> 00:20:13.940
I may have given in to every 
torture in my mind...

380
00:20:13.940 --> 00:20:15.240
What? All of them?

381
00:20:15.550 --> 00:20:20.060
But surrendering so many times beforehand 
has to have satisfied my desire to surrender!

382
00:20:17.860 --> 00:20:21.570
Desire to Surrender

383
00:20:20.060 --> 00:20:21.580
Desire to surrender?

384
00:20:21.810 --> 00:20:25.520
I'll never yield to today's torture!

385
00:20:25.870 --> 00:20:26.940
That'd be nice.

386
00:20:26.940 --> 00:20:28.700
What's with your reaction?!

387
00:20:28.700 --> 00:20:30.750
So you have no faith in me?

388
00:20:30.750 --> 00:20:32.850
I really <i>am</i> confident this time!

389
00:20:32.850 --> 00:20:33.920
I would even bet on it!

390
00:20:33.920 --> 00:20:34.920
For real?

391
00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:36.910
How about this?

392
00:20:37.190 --> 00:20:43.150
If I give in today, I'll get on my knees and 
beg Gilga to perform maintenance on you.

393
00:20:43.150 --> 00:20:43.930
What?!

394
00:20:43.930 --> 00:20:48.300
What's more, I'll even give up my futon 
and go to sleep in formal seiza posture!

395
00:20:48.300 --> 00:20:53.410
Well, I won't surrender, so there's 
no chance <i>that'll</i> ever happen!

396
00:20:55.310 --> 00:20:56.690
I beg you!

397
00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:50.470
Your Highness.

398
00:22:50.470 --> 00:22:54.330
I'll forget about you giving in, 
so please sleep on a futon.

399
00:22:54.730 --> 00:22:59.590
I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

400
00:22:59.590 --> 00:23:02.300
I won't go back on my word.

401
00:23:02.710 --> 00:23:03.920
Sure...

402
00:23:04.360 --> 00:23:07.550
By the way, were you having a nice dream?

403
00:23:07.550 --> 00:23:08.370
Huh?

404
00:23:08.370 --> 00:23:10.770
You looked like you were 
having fun in your sleep.

405
00:23:10.770 --> 00:23:11.970
While sitting in seiza.

406
00:23:15.030 --> 00:23:17.280
Yeah, I was.

407
00:23:18.010 --> 00:23:20.790
I had a dream about an old friend.

408
00:23:23.310 --> 00:23:24.640
An intruder!

409
00:23:24.640 --> 00:23:26.350
Get moving, guards!

410
00:23:30.650 --> 00:23:32.180
Stop right there!

411
00:23:32.760 --> 00:23:35.240
Who the hell are you?!

412
00:23:35.240 --> 00:23:37.260
What are you after?!

413
00:23:38.700 --> 00:23:43.700
